action_label: Take a walk through of AU Localisation Settings
description:
# AU Localisation Settings
Australian localisation Module will make the Tax Category in Customer, Supplier and Item (in Tax tab) Master mandatory. This setup can be switched off using the link in the section below. But it is suggested to keep it mandatory, so that BAS report can be generated without any issues.

BAS reports are configured to generate in a monthly frequency. This can be changed to Quarterly frequency using the link below.
name: Australia Localisation Settings
title: AU Localisation Settings
